script.name: plugin.guilds.cmd.docktend.menu
script.description: Guilds: Command script, Dock Tender - Menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds' $homebase = $a.obj -> get homebase $data = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='dock.trader'
*write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='Obj=%s, Event=%s, Data=%s', $a.obj, $a.event, $a.data, null, null
if $a.event == [MEvent.CmdCheck] if $homebase -> exists do if $homebase -> is of class Dock return [CmdConCheck.Available] do if $homebase -> is of class Headquarters return [CmdConCheck.Available] end return [CmdConCheck.Disabled]
else if $a.event == 'showmenu' START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.cmd.docktend.menu, value=$a.data return null
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] if not $data $data = table alloc $a.obj ->set local variable: name='dock.trader' value=$data end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Search] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.add' $data['search.ware'] = $selection gosub sub.BuyWare return $menu else if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.sell' $data['search.ware'] = $selection gosub sub.SellWare return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Switch] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.add' $data[$selection] = $value gosub sub.BuyWare return $menu else if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.sell' $data[$selection] = $value gosub sub.SellWare return $menu else if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.ware' $ware = $selection[2] $is.buy = $selection[1] $selection = $selection[0] if $is.buy $aWare = $data['buy.wares'][$ware] else $aWare = $data['sell.wares'][$ware] end if $selection == 'prio' inc $value = $aWare[1] = $value else if $selection == 'range' $aWare[2] = $value else if $selection == 'ship.qty' $aWare[5] = $value end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Hotkey] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $selection == 'info' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_WARE $input = create input: id='ware.info' encyclopedia page, ware=$value return $input end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Context] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.menu' if $value == 'info' if is datatype[ $selection ] == DATATYPE_WARE $input = create input: id='ware.info' encyclopedia page, ware=$selection return $input end else if $value == 'edit.buy' $is.buy = [TRUE] $ware = $selection gosub sub.EditWare return $input else if $value == 'edit.sell' $is.buy = [FALSE] $ware = $selection gosub sub.EditWare return $input else if $value == 'remove.buy' $data.wares = $data['buy.wares'] remove key $selection from table $data.wares gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $value == 'remove.sell' $data.wares = $data['sell.wares'] remove key $selection from table $data.wares gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.ware' $value = $a.data[3] if is datatype[ $selection ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $array = $selection $selection = $array[0] end
if $selection == 'price' $is.buy = $array[1] $ware = $array[2] if $is.buy $aWare = $data['buy.wares'][$ware] else $aWare = $data['sell.wares'][$ware] end $aWare[3] = $value play sample [Sound.Success] gosub sub.EditWare $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'qty' $is.buy = $array[1] $ware = $array[2] if $is.buy $aWare = $data['buy.wares'][$ware] else $aWare = $data['sell.wares'][$ware] end $aWare[4] = $value play sample [Sound.Success] gosub sub.EditWare $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end
else if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.menu' if $selection == 'clear.all' remove key 'buy.wares' from table $data remove key 'sell.wares' from table $data gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'add.all' gosub sub.AddAllWares gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $selection == 'save' $name = $data['name'] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4025 $input = create input: id='save.name', user input=Var/String, refobj=$a.obj, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$name return $input else if $selection == 'load' gosub sub.LoadSettings return $input end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'dock.tend.menu' if $selection == 'dock.tend.add' remove key 'search.ware' from table $data if $value do if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $value[0] $data.wares = $data['buy.wares'] if not $data.wares $data.wares = table alloc $data['buy.wares'] = $data.wares end if not $data.wares[$value] $ware = $value gosub sub.AddBuyWare end $is.buy = [TRUE] $ware = $value gosub sub.EditWare return $input end else if $selection == 'dock.tend.sell' remove key 'search.ware' from table $data if $value do if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $value[0] $data.wares = $data['sell.wares'] if not $data.wares $data.wares = table alloc $data['sell.wares'] = $data.wares end if not $data.wares[$value] $ware = $value gosub sub.AddSellWare end $is.buy = [FALSE] $ware = $value gosub sub.EditWare return $input end else if $selection == 'dock.tend.ware' gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $selection == 'dock.tend.load' if $value $Guild.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $tProfiles = $Guild.Data['docktend.profiles'] if $tProfiles $v = $tProfiles[$value] if $v $data = $v $a.obj ->set local variable: name='dock.trader' value=$data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end end else if $selection == 'save.name' if $value $data['name'] = $value $Guild.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $tProfiles = $Guild.Data['docktend.profiles'] if not $tProfiles $tProfiles = table alloc $Guild.Data['docktend.profiles'] = $tProfiles end $v = clone table $data $tProfiles[$value] = $v end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Arguments] $ret = create new array, arguments=$data, null, null, null, null return $ret
else if $a.event == 'dock.tend.menu' if $a.data == 'start' return [TRUE] end
else if $a.event == 'buy.ware' gosub sub.BuyWare return $input
else if $a.event == 'sell.ware' gosub sub.SellWare return $input end
return null
sub.AddAllWares: $tWares = $homebase ->get station tradeable ware table $buy.wares = $data['buy.wares'] if not $buy.wares $buy.wares = table alloc $data['buy.wares'] = $buy.wares end $sell.wares = $data['sell.wares'] if not $sell.wares $sell.wares = table alloc $data['sell.wares'] = $sell.wares end
if $tWares $ware = get next key: table=$tWares key=null while $ware $ware.flgs = get ware flags: ware=$ware if $ware.flgs & ( [WareType.Fluff] | [WareType.NoPrice] | [WareType.Dummy] | [WareType.Equipment] ) $ware = get next key: table=$tWares key=$ware continue end if $homebase ->is ware a tradeable: ware=$ware if not $buy.wares[$ware] gosub sub.AddBuyWare $v = $array[3] dec $v = $array[3] = $v end if not $sell.wares[$ware] gosub sub.AddSellWare end else if $homebase ->is ware a product: ware=$ware if not $buy.wares[$ware] gosub sub.AddBuyWare end else if $homebase ->is ware a resource: ware=$ware if not $sell.wares[$ware] gosub sub.AddSellWare end end $ware = get next key: table=$tWares key=$ware end end endsub
sub.LoadSettings: $menu = create custom menu array
$Guild.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $tProfiles = $Guild.Data['docktend.profiles'] if not $tProfiles $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else if not size of table $tProfiles $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $aSorted = sort table keys: table=$tProfiles $i = 0 $size = size of array $aSorted while $i < $size $name = $aSorted[$i] add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$name returnvalue=$name inc $i = end end
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4023 $input = create input: id='dock.tend.load' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
sub.AddBuyWare: gosub sub.AddWare $ware.max = $homebase -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay if $homebase -> is of class Headquarters $v = get relvalue of $ware $v = 240000 / $v do if $v < 4 $v = 4 $ware.max = get minimum, $ware.max, $v, null, null, null end $array[4] = $ware.max $data['buy.wares'][$ware] = $array endsub
sub.AddSellWare: gosub sub.AddWare $ware.min = $homebase ->get minimum storage: ware=$ware $array[4] = $ware.min $data['sell.wares'][$ware] = $array endsub
sub.AddWare: $array = array alloc: size=6 $array[0] = $ware $array[1] = 5 $v = $homebase ->get max buy jumps $array[2] = $v $v = $homebase -> get price of ware $ware $array[3] = $v $array[4] = 0 $array[5] = 9 endsub
sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4004 $text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=300 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4012 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-440 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4013 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-300 length=140 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4015 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-180 length=120 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4017 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-80 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4018 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[5] = $text add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.cols
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4006 $read.text = sprintf: fmt='[%s]', $read.text, null, null, null, null
add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text nextinput='buy.ware' value=null add section to custom menu: $menu
$data.wares = $data['buy.wares'] $is.buy = [TRUE] gosub sub.DrawWares
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4005 $text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=300 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4012 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-440 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4014 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-300 length=140 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4016 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-180 length=120 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4017 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-80 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4018 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[5] = $text add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.cols
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4011 $read.text = sprintf: fmt='[%s]', $read.text, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text nextinput='sell.ware' value=null add section to custom menu: $menu
$data.wares = $data['sell.wares'] $is.buy = [FALSE] gosub sub.DrawWares
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4019 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4020 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='clear.all' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4021 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='add.all' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret add section to custom menu: $menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4022 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='save' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='load' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4023 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret add section to custom menu: $menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4026 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue='start'
set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge] set menu option: $menu, icon=60
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4001 $input = create input: id='dock.tend.menu' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
sub.DrawWares: $drawn = [FALSE] if $data.wares $i = 0 $aSorted = sort table keys: table=$data.wares $size = size of array $aSorted while $i < $size $ware = $aSorted[$i] $aWare = $data.wares[$ware] gosub sub.DrawWareSide set menu line option: $menu, side menu=$side.menu $context = create context menu $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=29, returnvalue='info', hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] if $is.buy $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1108 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=18, returnvalue='edit.buy', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1107 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=66, returnvalue='remove.buy', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1108 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=18, returnvalue='edit.sell', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1107 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=66, returnvalue='remove.sell', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] end $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=818 add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$ware $ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$ware, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=300 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text $value = $aWare[1] $text = convert number $value to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-440 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $value = $aWare[3] $text = convert number $value to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-300 length=140 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text $value = $aWare[4] $text = convert number $value to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-180 length=120 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[3] = $text $value = $aWare[5] $value = ( $value + 1 ) * 5 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s%%', $value, null, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-80 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text $value = $aWare[2] $text = convert number $value to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=80 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[5] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret inc $i = end end endsub
sub.SellWare: $filter.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4003 $is.buy = [FALSE] $data.wares = $data['sell.wares'] gosub sub.GetWare endsub
sub.BuyWare: $filter.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4002 $is.buy = [TRUE] $data.wares = $data['buy.wares'] gosub sub.GetWare endsub
sub.DrawWareSide: $side.menu = create custom menu array set menu option: $side.menu, icon=20 set menu option: $side.menu, set title text=$ware $text = get ware description: ware=$ware add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text add info line section to menu: $side.menu
$read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9316 $text = get volume of ware $ware $text = convert number $text to string $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104408 $text = get transport class of ware $ware $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text add info line section to menu: $side.menu
$read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9510 $text = $homebase -> get price of ware $ware $text = convert number $text to string $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102527 $text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $ware.amt = $homebase -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.max = $homebase -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $percent = fixed multiply and divide: $ware.amt * 100 / $ware.max $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $text = convert number $ware.amt to string $text2 = convert number $ware.max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=90 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text.cols endsub
sub.GetWare: $menu = create custom menu array if $is.buy set menu option: $menu, icon=7 else set menu option: $menu, icon=53 end
$default = $data['filter.ware'] skip if $default $default = 0 $aValues = create new array, arguments=[Text.No], [Text.Yes], null, null, null add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$filter.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id='filter.ware', width=60 allowtabs=[FALSE] add section to custom menu: $menu
$tWares = $homebase ->get station tradeable ware table $drawn = [FALSE] if $tWares $search = $data['search.ware']
$aSorted = sort table keys: table=$tWares $size = size of array $aSorted $i = 0 while $i < $size $ware = $aSorted[$i] inc $i = $ware.flgs = get ware flags: ware=$ware do if $ware.flgs & ( [WareType.Fluff] | [WareType.NoPrice] | [WareType.Dummy] | [WareType.Equipment] ) continue
if $search if get length of string $search $text = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware, null, null, null, null skip if case insensitive string match, is $search in $text continue end end
if $default do if $homebase ->is ware for storage: ware=$ware continue if not $homebase ->is ware a tradeable: ware=$ware if $is.buy do if $homebase ->is ware a resource: ware=$ware continue else do if $homebase ->is ware a product: ware=$ware continue end end end
$is.disabled = [FALSE] if $data.wares do if $data.wares[$ware] $is.disabled = [TRUE] end
gosub sub.DrawWareSide set menu line option: $menu, side menu=$side.menu
$text.cols = array alloc: size=2 if $is.disabled $col = [MenuColour.Red] else $col = null end $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=$col text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text if $homebase ->is ware for storage: ware=$ware $text = 'Storage' else if $homebase ->is ware a tradeable: ware=$ware $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104519 else if $homebase ->is ware a product: ware=$ware $text = 'Product' else if $homebase ->is ware a resource: ware=$ware $text = 'Resource' else $text = '-' end $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text if $is.disabled $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id=$ware else $ret = $ware end
add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret $drawn = [TRUE] end end
if not $drawn $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text end
set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.Identity], id='info' set menu option: $menu, allow searching=[TRUE]
if $is.buy $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4004 $input = create input: id='dock.tend.add' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$homebase callback=[Callback.Switch] else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4005 $input = create input: id='dock.tend.sell' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$homebase callback=[Callback.Switch] end endsub
sub.EditWare: if $is.buy $aWare = $data['buy.wares'][$ware] else $aWare = $data['sell.wares'][$ware] end
$menu = create custom menu array set menu option: $menu, icon=65
if $is.buy $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=23 else $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=21 end $ware.min = get min price of ware $ware $ware.max = get max price of ware $ware $default = $aWare[3] $text = convert number $default to string $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text $ret = create new array, arguments='price', $is.buy, $ware, null, null $ret = create menu return value: callback, value=$ret add price trade bar to menu: $menu, text=$text, min=$ware.min, max=$ware.max, current=$default, return value=$ret
$ware.max = $homebase -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $default = $aWare[4] if $is.buy $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4008 else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4029 end $ret = create new array, arguments='qty', $is.buy, $ware, null, null $ret = create menu return value: callback, value=$ret $text = convert number $default to string $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add trade bar to menu: $menu, text=$text, min=1, max=$ware.max, current=$default, return value=$ret, left text=' ', right text='%CURRENT%'
$aValues = array alloc: size=21 $i = 0 while $i < 21 $value = ( $i + 1 ) * 5 $value = sprintf: fmt='%s%%', $value, null, null, null, null $aValues[$i] = $value inc $i = end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4009 $default = $aWare[5] $ret = create new array, arguments='ship.qty', $is.buy, $ware, null, null add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id=$ret, width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE]
add section to custom menu: $menu
$aValues = array alloc: size=10 $i = 0 while $i < 10 $value = $i + 1 $aValues[$i] = $value inc $i = end $default = $aWare[1] dec $default = $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4010 $ret = create new array, arguments='prio', $is.buy, $ware, null, null add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id=$ret, width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE] $aValues = array alloc: size=21 $i = 0 while $i < 19 $aValues[$i] = $i inc $i = end $default = $aWare[2] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=24 $ret = create new array, arguments='range', $is.buy, $ware, null, null add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id=$ret, width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE]
gosub sub.DrawWareSide set menu option: $menu, default side menu=$side.menu set menu option: $menu, maximum menu height=16 lines
if $is.buy $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4004 else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=4005 end $callback = [Callback.Switch] $input = create input: id='dock.tend.ware' menu=$menu title=$ware description=$read.text callback=$callback endsub
return null
